thread.title: Adrian Papi
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Adrian Papi

author: Adrian Papi
title: Adrian Papi
text: Great tracking. Reliable. Pricing of service represents good value. After using a cheap carrier a week or so ago who did not properly scan or track my parcel and who damaged the electronic gear in the package, I'm really happy with Pack and Send. As long as items are properly packed they always deliver safely and timely.
